When updating, change these files (if needed):

- VERSION
- ChangeLog (**)
- AUTHORS
- CREDITS
- src/text.c (years in Copyright lines near EOF)
- run: make man/axel.1
- run: make -C po update-po


When done:

- run: make relcheck
- run: make distcheck
- test Debian packaging
- make a pull-request


(**) $ ./mkchangelog
